{"ts":"2026-07-18T10:08:19.334Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-cj9v"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"GH-589: pm next --assignee X answers from anonymous-caller perspective and pm claim conflates assignment with claim"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"GitHub issue #589, two conflations breaking multi-agent coordinator queries: (a) pm next --assignee X without --author X relegates X's own claimable work to held_by_others (empty ready/recommended) — asking about X should adopt X's perspective or the envelope should say why rows were held out; (b) pm claim on an assigned-but-never-claimed item errors 'already claimed by <assignee>' though no claim ever happened — assignment and claim are distinct lifecycle facts and the recovery hint should name assignment takeover explicitly."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-ux","cli","multi-agent"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-18T10:08:19.334Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-18T10:08:19.334Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":240},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"pm next --assignee X surfaces X's claimable work as ready/recommended (or discloses the perspective rule in the envelope); claim on assigned-unclaimed items distinguishes assignment from claim in error text and recovery hints; contract docs define assignee-vs-author-vs-claim semantics; regression coverage for both conflations"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-mpbb"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"medium"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/dependencies","value":[{"id":"pm-8t5x","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-18T10:08:19.334Z"},{"id":"pm-h90s","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-18T10:08:19.334Z"},{"id":"pm-w8q4","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-18T10:08:19.334Z"}]}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"16350cd767dcd5de7b847868e804e7a562faa493fca5d63aeca9326f313301c0","message":""}
